text.__SUMMARY__: Corydoras garbei is a species of catfish in the family Callichthyidae endemic to Brazil where it is found in the São Francisco River basin.  It is sold as an aquarium fish.
text.References: Froese, Rainer and Pauly, Daniel, eds. (2011). "Corydoras garbei" in FishBase. December 2011 version.
